org.pepstock.charba.client.resources

Interface Resources<T extends com.google.gwt.resources.client.ResourcePrototype>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - resources prototype type of CHART.JS resource
    All Superinterfaces:
    com.google.gwt.resources.client.ClientBundle
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DeferredResources, EmbeddedResources

    public interface Resources<T extends com.google.gwt.resources.client.ResourcePrototype>
extends com.google.gwt.resources.client.ClientBundle
    Client bundle to reference CHART.JS and other java script codes, always needed to CHARBA.
    CHART.JS text resource it's just defined because the mode how to inject depends on the implementation of this interface. It includes some image resources for datasets items selector plugin, the same for all implementation.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
    See Also:
    DeferredResources, EmbeddedResources
